        <item>
            <title>【评测】RG RX-78-2 元祖高达 2.0     资深模型师评语：感觉似 PGU 缩细版</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/rgrx782-0/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=rgrx782-0</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/rgrx782-0/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 12:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257151</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日模型界的热门话题，一定是 Bandai 的 RG RX-78-2 元祖高达 2.0 推出了，当年 Bandai 推出 RG 系列的首个作品，也就是 RG RX-78-2 元祖高达，当时也是非常哄动！玩具模型都是早买早享受，小编收到送测版时已是今日的事了，但上星期已有很多模型发烧友或高手早已入手，亦已见到有很多完成作品在各高达或模型群组分享，故此小编也邀请了一位资深模型师 N.Maker 熊沛文先生，品评一下这部 RG RX-78-2 元祖高达 2.0。</p><h2>超简单开箱</h2><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257226" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0736-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0736-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0736.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">今日收到送测的大热 RG 2.0 元祖高达了。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0737-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0737-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0737.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">今次的胶贴纸比较少花纹，但有字的贴纸就比较多。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0738-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0738-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0738.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">素组派应该会比较喜爱的隐藏式水口。</p><h2>资深模型师的品评</h2><p>小编邀请了资深模型师 N.Maker 熊沛文先生，他是 2023 年第 11 届高达模型王 GBWC 大赛香港区 OVER-21 组别冠军，亦担任 2024 年第 12 届高达模型王 GBWC 大赛香港区颁奖嘉宾。见到他上星期已素组了，由他品评一下这部 RG RX-78-2 元祖高达 2.0 就最好不过。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257231" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7999bbbfca1041e1bd45-479x580.jpg" alt="" width="479" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7999bbbfca1041e1bd45-479x580.jpg 479w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7999bbbfca1041e1bd45.jpg 743w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 479px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">深模型师 N.Maker 熊沛文先生</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257232" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6fe536648e3747edb868-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6fe536648e3747edb868-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6fe536648e3747edb868.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">担任 2024 年第 12 届高达模型王 GBWC 大赛香港区颁奖嘉宾</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257233" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6a8d72bcc99c474bac97-433x580.jpg" alt="" width="433" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6a8d72bcc99c474bac97-433x580.jpg 433w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6a8d72bcc99c474bac97.jpg 673w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 433px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">开箱！真香！</p><p>RG RX-78-2 元祖高达 2.0 素组完成后，外观像是 2020 年推出的 PGU 缩小版，比起 RG 1.0 版更加强壮扎实，关节的松紧度非常适中，不再有以前 RG 1.0 那种松散的感觉，能够轻松地摆动而不必担心损坏。<a title="DSC08609" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933045988/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933045988_8a2794a6d2_h.jpg" alt="DSC08609" width="1280" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08614" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53931900537/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53931900537_f643e2dcd5_h.jpg" alt="DSC08614" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>特别值得一提的是腰部和双脚的可动性设计非常精彩，即使在有核心战机的情况下，腰部仍然可以大幅度弯曲，这是非常值得赞赏的设计。而双脚在弯曲时，整个脚部的装甲会随之连动，这么小的比例却能做到这样的结构，非常厉害。</p><p><a title="DSC08585" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933046118/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933046118_5ab6bf68f7_h.jpg" alt="DSC08585" width="1280" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08589" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933136224/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933136224_a7078f2f75_h.jpg" alt="DSC08589" width="1281" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08592" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933046113/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933046113_8dd22c9426_h.jpg" alt="DSC08592" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此外，在组装时你会发现零件很少有传统柱形的插槽，这使得每个零件和装甲都可以轻松组装，但又不影响松紧度，这大大提高了组装的乐趣。然而，这款模型的头部偏大，有些影响整体外观比例。另外，废除了可动手掌，仅提供了造型手和造型拳头，但拳头比例偏小，显得不够协调。而小腿也无法完全伸直，使得站立摆姿势时有轻微弯曲的感觉。</p><p><a title="DSC08598" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933136144/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933136144_ea0be413c1_h.jpg" alt="DSC08598" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08599" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53932804936/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53932804936_938b93f149_h.jpg" alt="DSC08599" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08600" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933136134/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933136134_30f310d431_h.jpg" alt="DSC08600" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>最近网上有讨论头部火炮露出的幅度不够，与官方图片不一致。经过观察，确实有这个现象，火炮大约差 0.1 至 0.2 毫米才能完全露出。不过，无论从远看还是细看，都不算大问题，大部分玩家可能根本不会注意到这点。所以，享受模型的整体设计和组装乐趣才是最重要的，千万别让这些细微差距破坏了你的快乐。当然，Bandai 如何回应这个问题是另一回事。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257236" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/snap0046-694x447.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="447" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/snap0046-694x447.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/snap0046.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这套模型在不需要复杂组装的前提下，依然做出了出色的结构设计，是一个值得购买的产品。回想十几年前 Bandai 推出 RG RX-78-2 时，已经觉得那款模型非常惊艳。十几年后再做 RG 2.0，组装过程中勾起了当年初次体验的回忆，这真是见证时代变迁的一种感觉。</p><p><a title="DSC08603" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933136119/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933136119_fa457546bc_h.jpg" alt="DSC08603" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="DSC08608" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53932804846/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53932804846_0361d4950f_h.jpg" alt="DSC08608" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="DSC08621" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53932804766/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53932804766_9f3ed93db3_h.jpg" alt="DSC08621" width="1280" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="DSC08625" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933252805/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933252805_7fe0c69b9b_h.jpg" alt="DSC08625" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Freel%2F347474625101048%2F&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=267&amp;t=0" width="267" height="476" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p><strong>RG 1/144 RX-78-2 高达 Ver.2.0</strong><br />
参考售价：3,850 日圆（含税）</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/rgrx782-0/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/">【评测】RG RX-78-2 元祖高达 2.0     资深模型师评语：感觉似 PGU 缩细版</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
