        <item>
            <title>彭博：Apple 将推两款 AirPods 4     具降噪功能平价版随 iPhone 16 发布</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/airpods4/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=airpods4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/airpods4/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 11:00:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AirPods 2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AirPods 3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AirPods 4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257054</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>有消息指 Apple 将于今年推出两款 AirPods 系列产品，以取代 AirPods 2 及 AirPods 3，并随 iPhone 16 系列及全新 Apple Watch 于下月的秋季发布会中推出。</p><p>2019 年推出的 AirPods 2 与第一代 AirPods 极为相似，属于入门级耳机，售价仅为港币$1099；而 2021 年推出、售港币$1399 的 AirPods 3 则支援空间音讯、触控感应器、支援 Apple Watch 充电等多项升级功能。</p><p>Bloomberg 记者 Mark Gurman 报道指，Apple 计划推出两款 AirPods 4 以取代入门级的 AirPods 2 及 AirPods 3，将采用现代化设计并升级现有功能。他表示两款全新 AirPods 4 的设计相似，皆采用 USB-C 充电，但只有价格较高的 AirPods 4 会支援主动降噪 (ANC) 技术及无线充电功能。Mark Gurman 指价格较高的 AirPods 4 只是 AirPods 及 AirPods Pro 之间的桥梁，而非 AirPods Pro。</p><p>他重申 Apple 尚未落实 AirPods 4 的计划，或有可能将入门级 AirPods 命名为 AirPods Lite，而价格较高的机款则命名为 AirPods 4。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.business-standard.com/technology/tech-news/apple-may-launch-two-new-airpods-alongside-iphone-16-series-in-september-124081900318_1.html">Business Standard</a>、<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/08/18/gurman-airpods-4-still-coming-this-fall-in-two-new-variants/">9To5Mac</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/apple-intelligence-7-functions/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学+实试】Apple Intelligence 7 大实用功能　一键校对英文文法 + TLDR 长文总结 + 录音即时转文字</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/iphone-clear-cache-2024/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】帮 iPhone 清除 IG、FB 无用垃圾　实试释放手机 16 GB 储存容量</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安装方法 + 申请教学</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/airpods4/mobile-music/headphones/">彭博：Apple 将推两款 AirPods 4     具降噪功能平价版随 iPhone 16 发布</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
