        <item>
            <title>Apple 发布无障碍主题短片《接力赛》   iPhone、Apple Watch 助残疾运动员生活及比赛</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/apple-62/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-62</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/apple-62/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:00:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[无障碍功能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[辅助功能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257041</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>随著奥运落幕和残奥会临近，Apple 近日发布一条有关无障碍主题的短片《接力赛》，讲述八位残疾和非残疾运动员比赛的故事，当中提到的无障碍功能突显 Apple 的多元性，为每个人的不同而设计。</p><p>继早前的《The Greatest》及《丢失的声音》，Apple 最近于官网及 YouTube 上载无障碍主题短片《接力赛》。片中的运动员使用 Apple 各款产品配合其日常生活、训练及比赛，当中内置的视力、听力、肢体活动能力、认知能力及语音等无障碍功能能配合不同用户的需要。他们亦使用各种功能来追踪表现，如睡眠指标、每日锻炼目标及全天运动情况。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257045" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-2-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-2-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-4-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-4-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-4-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-5-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257048" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-5-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-5-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-5-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>影片提到 iPhone 「朗读内容」、Apple Watch 「辅助触控」、iPhone 「放大镜」+「指住即读」、Apple Watch 「轮椅体能训练」，分别可为有视障的用户大声朗读文字、上肢残障用户在不接触萤幕的情况下使用 Apple Watch、大声读出视障用户指向附近实物上的文字，以及为轮椅用户提供两种独特的运动追踪选项。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-694x368.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="368" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-694x368.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257044" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-1-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-1-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-3-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257046" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-3-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-3-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-8-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257051" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-8-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-8-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-8-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>此外，Apple 将于今年秋季推出全新辅助功能，利用硬件和软件为残障用户创造全新的直观体验，当中包括「音乐触觉」让听障碍用户在 iPhone 上体验音乐；「语音捷径」和「侦测非典型语音」能增强语音识别和度身订造功能，适用于更多非典型语音用户；「眼动追踪」让身障用户只用眼睛就能使用 iPhone 和 iPad 等。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_52703"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BPqir3EZolw?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>图片来源：影片截图</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/accessibility/the-relay/">Apple</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/apple-intelligence-7-functions/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学+实试】Apple Intelligence 7 大实用功能　一键校对英文文法 + TLDR 长文总结 + 录音即时转文字</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安装方法 + 申请教学</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/27/apple-vision-pro-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%a1%8c%e8%b2%a8%e5%85%a8%e6%94%bb%e7%95%a5-%e5%bf%85%e8%a3%9d-app-%e3%80%81-%e6%b8%af%e7%89%88%e7%89%b9%e8%89%b2%e3%80%81%e5%a4%a7%e9%99%b8%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Vision Pro 香港行货全攻略 :  必装 APP 、 港版特色、大陆使用、近视及老花用家、预订注意、开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/apple-62/mobile-phone/">Apple 发布无障碍主题短片《接力赛》   iPhone、Apple Watch 助残疾运动员生活及比赛</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
